[normal]              
[normal]Deploying CCS on a large
[normal] scale
[normal] will require 
[normal]policy certainty 
[normal]through a combination of 
[normal]carbon pricing, direct financial support 
[normal]for research and development (particularly for more advanced capture technologies for gas and biomass power plants and for industrial applications)
