[normal] the UK can
[normal] 
[normal]lead the way
[normal].
[normal] A
[normal] key technical challenge 
[normal]is
[normal] 
[normal]to 
[normal]integrat
[normal]e
[normal] all 
[normal]of 
[normal]the various sub-systems
[normal], and to 
[normal]ensure that they operate
[normal] efficiently
[normal] togethe
[normal]r and
[normal], subsequently, 
[normal]within 
[normal]a network. In particular, 
[normal]an 
[normal]understanding 
[normal]of 
[normal]how CCS 
[normal]can
[normal] operate 
[normal]most effectively within 
[normal]a diverse energy system will be of particular value.
